entry.title: Dark Reader for Safari
entry.content:
优惠信息（价格：USD 4.99 → USD 1.99 [USD 1.99 ~ USD 7.99]）

全部价格信息

价格：USD 1.99

应用描述

Dark Reader is an eye-care Safari extension that enables night mode by creating dark themes for websites on the fly. It inverts bright colors to make web pages high contrast and easier to read. Dark Reader integrates seamlessly with system dark mode. Adjust brightness and contrast to match your display and ambient lighting. Enable dark mode on every web page or give websites a sepia tone. Select from multiple color theme presets or create your own by customizing background and text colors. Enable or disable Dark Reader for specific websites, automatically sync with system dark mode, or detect already dark websites and leave them unchanged. Developed by the original creators of Dark Reader. Since 2014, we continuously evolve alongside modern web technologies to deliver fast and reliable dark mode support for people sensitive to bright light. A single purchase includes access to the macOS version (Safari browser) when using the same iCloud account. Dark Reader contains no ads and does not collect user data. Enable Dark Reader in Safari preferences and disable similar extensions to prevent conflicts. Enjoy browsing!

全部价格信息

应用描述

Are you ready to become the ultimate screw master? Welcome to Screw Pin Jam Puzzle: Wood, the most addictive and fun screw puzzle game of the year! If you are a fan of logic puzzles, brain teasers, and the satisfying sound of wood, this game is made for you. Dive into a world of challenging mechanics where your mission is simple yet tricky: unscrew the pins, remove the nuts and bolts, and clear the wood plates to solve the jam. It sounds easy, but as you progress, the levels become a true IQ test! KEY FEATURES: Engaging Gameplay: Enjoy the classic mechanic of nuts and bolts. Strategically unscrew the pins to make the wood bars fall. Wood Theme & ASMR: Immerse yourself in the relaxing world of wood. From simple warm-ups to complex hard puzzles, challenge your mind every day. Custom Skins: Unlock unique skins for your screws, nuts, and bolts. Customize your board for a fresh experience. Global Leaderboard: Compete with friends and players worldwide to see who solves the screw jam the fastest. HOW TO PLAY: Tap to unscrew the nuts and bolts from the wood plates. Move the screws to the empty holes strategically to avoid a pin jam. Drop all the wood plates to clear the level and win rewards. Use hints if you get stuck on a tricky screw puzzle. Whether you want to relax after a long day or challenge your brain with a tough logic game, Screw Pin Jam Puzzle: Wood is the perfect choice. Experience the thrill of solving the ultimate wood puzzle! Download now and start unscrewing! Can you solve the jam?
